# Drop a 1024×1024 PNG named `icon.png` here before running `pnpm tauri build`.
# Tauri also wants 32×32 / 128×128 / [email protected]; the easiest path is:
#
#     pnpm tauri icon path/to/source.png
#
# Until then the placeholder embedded PNG in `src/main.rs::default_icon()` keeps
# `tauri dev` running.
